flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: New shipment request or detected risk event in the transportation network.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve shipment details from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: AutoML - Analyze shipment details for HazMat compliance.]
  N2 --> N3{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Select optimal routes and carriers based on compliance and cost.}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions - Generate customs declarations and optimize clearance time.]
  N4 --> N5[Cortex: Data Quality & Validation - Monitor carrier safety and compliance records.]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Process Builder - Execute incident response plans if necessary.]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced compliance delays, minimized COGS impact, improved on-time delivery, and reduced working capital tied to risk events.]
  N3 -->|Carrier fails safety compliance check.| B1[Escalate to compliance team for further action.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Carrier utilization decision deferred to compliance team.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Oversize permit required but not avai...| B2[Re-route shipment or delay until permit is obtained.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Shipment re-routed or delayed to ensure compliance.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Incident occurs during transportation.| B3[Trigger incident response plan and update shipment status.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Incident handled and shipment status updated accordingly.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]